name: Salma Hayek LoRA
description:
A Stable Diffusion LoRA profile.

More available on my site: https://ko-fi.com/diffusionbox

Place it in "stable-diffusion-webui\extensions\sd-webui-additional-networks\models\lora" folder in Automatic1111 WebUI root folder.

Made using kohya-ss so make sure to have that extension installed!

In txt2img, under "Additional Networks", select "Enable" and under Model 1 select "" and assign a weight between 0.3-0.7 (feel free to experiment!). In the promt text window use "" within your promt to generate images.

Embed has been trained on Stable Diffusion 1.5 model.

I Recommend the model https://civitai.com/models/4922/grapelikedreamfruit - Gives amazing realistic renders.

Your output will vary depending upon your prompt, negative prompt, model, VAE, and Hypernetworks used.

More available on my site: https://ko-fi.com/diffusionbox
